  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"sGlLEyWh\">泻药。与其说<b>“改变”刻板印象</b>不如说<b>“减少”刻板印象</b>。</p><p data-pid=\"eiQFiAQr\">比如，对于女性的刻板印象从“三从四德”变成“小公举”“女司机”“广场舞大妈”，仍然是一种性别隔离的视角，只不过有色眼镜的领域和方式换了。</p><p data-pid=\"oaaMpWau\">事实上，男性和女性的性格更多是社会塑造的，两性在绝大多数领域的潜能和天赋是大同小异的，只有不再因为性别而先入为主地说一个人“应该是怎样”，才能真正地让每一个人不再受到刻板印象的枷锁，发挥出自己的最大潜力。</p><p data-pid=\"dnwyto59\">最后致敬<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=199221592&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E9%9D%92%E4%BA%91&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">青云<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>姐姐，她好美！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-47b48f2cfa17e78af8b31b3bbf855bc3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1262\" data-rawheight=\"984\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-0a143744aca2306d0968b920ce64bc8b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-20124722e36462130fcf9cdda5c5e924_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1262\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-47b48f2cfa17e78af8b31b3bbf855bc3_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1262' height='984'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1262\" data-rawheight=\"984\" data-size=\"no